- "section":    a divider/section header. Fields: "title".
- "bullets":    a few concise bullet points. Fields: "title", "bullets" (array of short strings), optional "notes" (speaker notes).
- "image_text": a short explanatory slide. Fields: "title", optional "body" (a sentence or two), optional "bullets", optional "notes".
- "chart":      a data chart. Fields: "title", optional "caption", and "spec" — an AntV Infographic DSL string using a chart-* template.
- "infographic":a visual infographic. Fields: "title", optional "caption", and "spec" — an AntV Infographic DSL string using a NON-chart template.

